    <h2>What separates our dispenser service from general ice machine repair.</h2>

    <ul class="reasons-list">
      <li><strong>Vend mechanism expertise.</strong> Actuators, solenoids, and agitators are dispenser-specific components that don't exist on production ice machines. General ice-machine techs sometimes misdiagnose dispenser issues. We don't.</li>
